data.title: UNICOM Engineering honored Dell OEM Solutions Partner Award
data.meta_description: Winner of the coveted Partner of the Year Award for the third year running
data.text:
Winner of the coveted Partner of the Year Award for the third year running

Canton, MA – December 15, 2021 — UNICOM Engineering, a leading strategic system integration partner providing application platforms, deployment solutions, and lifecycle support services for software technology developers and OEMs worldwide, today announced it was honored to receive the Dell Technologies OEM Solutions North America Partner of the Year Award for the third consecutive year.
